Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:34.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Kenryu and the rest\Ntried to keep it from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:37.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo was well aware of\NGyokaku Kumoi's true intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo returned to\Nthe Soul Society alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:42.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and his friends went
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:44.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,after her and broke into the \NKasumiohji Clan mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,hoping to rescue Rurichiyo\Nduring the marriage ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But they fell into Kumoi's trap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:51.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and were surrounded by\NSoi Fon and her squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:56.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With help from Shu Kannogi,\NRurichiyo's fiancé,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:59.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they managed to escape from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:03.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But now Ichigo is wanted by\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:12.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Found them?\N– No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Search over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:15.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a deep wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:29.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that there was
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:34.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a place like this underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you go through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:39.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:43.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But we must find Ruricchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:44.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:48.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers have widened\Ntheir search above ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go now,\Nwe'll surely be captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:51.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:53.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:56.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have any idea\Nwhere Rurichiyo might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:03.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never walked\Noutside the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen the outside while being
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:09.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,carried inside my palanquin though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all aristocrats like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:15.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruricchi used to sneak out\Nonce in a while it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm such a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put yourself down too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:24.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be somewhere inside
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Kasumiohji Clan mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's infiltrate one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:30.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sir Kenryu has been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we manage by ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu, at least you know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:38.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the inside of the mansion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:40.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:42.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so huge that \NI don't know it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:47.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:56.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Groups Three and Four
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:58.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,have spread out\Nto the mansion grounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but we haven't found them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Groups One and Two have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:05.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Groups Five and Six have left\Nto switch places with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Continue your search.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry… Can you give me some time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We received\NSquad 3's scheduled report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Found them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:32.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:37.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But those guys, Kenryu and Enryu…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Was handing them to the Kasumiohji Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:40.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:43.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should have kept them\Nin custody ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:45.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:46.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Captain's orders are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to let the nobles take care\Nof their own problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:02.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission is to capture\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to mobilize\Nthe Punishment Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unraveling the truth can come later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 3 has been ordered to stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:23.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take turns in groups to take your meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Group One, eat first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– How are things on this side?\N– Make it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:29.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you \Nstay on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai. You're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:35.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I left the rest to Squad 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:36.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:42.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is going\Nto take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be pretty strong too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:47.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:49.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Kibune acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:56.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's nothing, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It never feels good to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,have suspicions\Ntoward your teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:07.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:11.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:12.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:29.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Have emergency repairs been made\Nto the damaged wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:30.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We do not know when those bandits\Nmay break in again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to keep a tight watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So they slipped away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Thirteen Court Guard Squads\Nare useless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kumoi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,About Lady Rurichiyo's meals…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Her room is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess is closeted in her room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,due to today's disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No meal is necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:02.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of the princess,\Nwhose marriage ceremony was disrupted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:05.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… I beg your pardon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:10.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hadn't counted on Shu Kannogi\Nbeing taken hostage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:12.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh well. No matter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In any case the princess\Nis in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! The princess?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, sir! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She passed through\Nthe Senkaimon and is headed this way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:29.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have a close watch on\Nthe Precipice World!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have preparations already been made?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:49.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, to the grand hall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, join the princess!{\i1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let us celebrate with a toast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:58.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}– Right!\N– Right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there no gatekeeper today?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have come back to this place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How small the sky appears,\Nnow that I look at it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone… Someone help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:34.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend\Nto keep me locked up in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let you out shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we deal with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Substitute Soul Reaper \Nwho came after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…came after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:56.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he disrupted\Nthe marriage ceremony and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,made an enemy of\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:02.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Kumoi hire you for money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very simplistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:16.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a cheap man who'd hire out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,his life just for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:21.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are you so scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:24.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:29.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know much about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:34.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you are deathly\Nafraid of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:35.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That much I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:36.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:48.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be acting\Nso brave much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:02.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Hey, Third Seat Kibune!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:07.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you up to at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:09.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:11.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be\Non emergency alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:19.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I just had a little.\NPlease keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't tell anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:26.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,what Third Seat Kibune was doing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:34.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:38.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:39.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:44.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And a squad member went\Nmissing last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:49.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well… It seems a few members
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,were secretly drinking last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:57.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them noticed someone\Nresembling Third Seat Kibune
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and went after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:02.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And he didn't return after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:03.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, go and look for Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take direct command of the search
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,for the Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:17.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a good feeling\Nabout this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the search under\Nyour command.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be some reason for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they'd act this way\Nwithout a good reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they do, what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:50.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We show no mercy to anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who defies the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the search under\Nyour command.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:06.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting me in charge\Nof everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Renji Abarai,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:14.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,will take command\Nof Squad 6 and set out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:37.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we been found?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're okay for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:43.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, we've been discovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:54.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:57.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– After them!\N– Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:58.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be around there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If Hanataro were here,\Nwe'd know our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:10.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's a dead-end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:15.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to meet up\Nin a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:39.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. It's sheer coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:43.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That top coat. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:47.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen Court Guard Squads…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:51.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 3 Captain, Shusuke Amagai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 3 Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:03.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A new captain\Nwho was recently appointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:07.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder he looked unfamiliar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were some other captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:14.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've reasoned with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Ichigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I must arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rukia Kuchiki of Squad 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:35.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hear us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:40.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you'll submit and come\N \Nwith us to the barracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:41.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:47.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, take care of Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:56.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the rumored skills\Nof the Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:37.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone so big,\Nyou move pretty nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not someone\NI can beat half-heartedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sever…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:56.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Raika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle gets serious from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Suits me fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on,\Ncome on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all, Substitute Soul Reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:18:01.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsuga…tensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:19.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Stop!\N– Sir Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:44.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your marriage ceremony\Nwas ruined by him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,on top of which he took you hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So why would you protect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:54.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I chose to go with them\Nunder my own will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:59.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Captain, please hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:00.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:07.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,These people saved Ruricchi's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:15.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to\Nhelp out Ruricchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:18.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:24.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But they helped open my eyes\Nand I want to save Ruricchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:29.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this.\NThe Kasumiohji Clan is in dire straits now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Shu…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:31.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:36.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So please help us find Ruricchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:46.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:48.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:49.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing a face like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:51.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it took away my interest \Nin doing battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Put away your swords too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:55.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Internal strife in the Kasumiohji Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:06.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And you were hired to be bodyguards?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:07.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:16.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that it's the\N Kasumiohji Clan is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:19.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the Head Captain is hesitant
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to stick his nose into their affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:25.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's a matter of jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless there's concrete evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:32.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,or some excuse to get involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:35.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There is. The Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakkouto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:40.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The weapons they use.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:43.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is definitely illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:46.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, to just take over a clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it is way too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:53.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And? What do you guys\Nintend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're searching for the place\NRurichiyo is being kept.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:59.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who participated in\Nthe marriage ceremony was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:03.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find Lady Rurichiyo and\Nexpose Kumoi's crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:08.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, Sir Shu is now on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:11.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:15.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we'll help you\Nrescue Princess Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:18.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Captain!\N– Can he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Their story seems sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:31.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I had some issues too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I think siding with you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:36.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,will clear up this \Nincident more quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:40.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inform Kira about this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:41.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so glad. Ruricchi, just wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're coming to save you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:21.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I come to the Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:23.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:25.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hide somewhere for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:28.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:28.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:29.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:31.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My older brother is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:33.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops… That's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:34.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:36.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:39.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get more snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:40.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:43.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:45.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The door won't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:53.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit to the hidden room\Nhas been sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:55.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That should…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:23:59.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakki, too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:02.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another door here too!